entries.femaleVariant: Didn't notice any effects till the second or third day.
They didn't detect a thing? They just gave you overtime?
Listen, they even asked if I wanted a second shift, 'cause the system detected "additional energy resources" in me.
I'm telling you, those boosters are a miracle. Go see that ripper, tell him I sent you. He'll give you a discount.
Side effects? Girl, I'm done reading all that fine print. Waste of time.
